{
  "stem": "24195.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So we, [LAUGHS] we wound up standing almost immediately directly across from the reviewing stand where Hitler and his high officers and, and, and rest of his government were standing and reviewing the parade.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the thing that struck me-- you know, we were supposed to cheer, too.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Every time the flags would come by, you know, we were-- everybody cheered.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But the thing that amazed me was that Hitler was constantly standing and holding up his arm like this and never-- that was like a four-, five-hour parade.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, we were all getting pretty darn tired.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here, this man was standing there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, I can't remember if he ever left his arm down, which we were starting-- we were starting to make jokes about it.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, is he a Superman?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How can anybody be like this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe he's a robot, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And somebody suggested he might have a spring installed under his-- [LAUGHS] in his armpit that he would be able.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it certainly was very impressive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was certainly impressive to the German people and the-- walking by of all those German Army divisions.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not very-- not very friendly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I was-- you know, but I have no choice.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had to be there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If I wasn't going to be there, you couldn't, you know, just duck out and-- unless you played sick or something.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that, you know-- and people would not believe it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I remember that it was difficult.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- a very ironic thing was that I became friendly-- because we lived in the same neighborhood, and we had to walk back-- back and forth-- back and to school every day together.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was in-- you know, this is not like today, when children are constantly driven to school.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
